<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="感通" xml:id="gsz0845b09shiChangYu"><lb
ed="T" n="0845b09"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0845b09"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000005495"><placeName>清涼山</placeName><placeName>祕魔巖</placeName></placeName><persName key="A004846">常遇</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0845b10"/><persName key="A004846">釋常遇</persName>，俗姓<name>陰</name>，<placeName key="PL000000000368"><anchor xml:id="beg0845sgsz1"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>苑</sic><corr>范</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0845sgsz1"/>陽</placeName>人也，出家於<placeName key="PL000000000514">燕</placeName>北<placeName key="PL000000000496">安集<lb
ed="T" n="0845b11"/>寺</placeName>。襟懷灑落，道貌清奇，晦跡林泉，避脫聲<lb
ed="T" n="0845b12"/>利<ptr target="#n2719"/>。<date from-iso="+0850-02-20" key="j20315672031920" to-iso="+0851-02-08"><name>大中</name>四年</date>，<anchor xml:id="beg0845002"/>杖錫<anchor xml:id="end0845002"/>離<placeName key="PL000000000514">燕</placeName>，孤征朔雪，祁冱<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1784"/>千<lb
ed="T" n="0845b13"/>里，徑涉<placeName key="PL000000005250">五峯</placeName>，詣<placeName key="PL000000005387"><placeName>華嚴寺</placeName><placeName>菩薩堂</placeName></placeName>，矚<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>睟<lb
ed="T" n="0845b14"/>容，施右手中指，沃以香膏，爇以星焰，光騰<lb
ed="T" n="0845b15"/>半日，怡顏宛然。次遍遊聖境，終始兩朞<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1274"/>，其所<lb
ed="T" n="0845b16"/>覩祥瑞，不可勝紀。後至<placeName key="PL000000005491">西臺</placeName>，遇古聖跡<lb
ed="T" n="0845b17"/>曰<placeName key="PL000000005495">祕魔巖</placeName>，乃<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>降龍之處也<ptr target="#n2720"/>。<persName key="A004846">遇</persName>稽首之際，<lb
ed="T" n="0845b18"/>忽見輕雲金光，爛爛駭目，漸分雉堞<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1785"/>，方勢<lb
ed="T" n="0845b19"/>如城──咸曰「金色世界」也<ptr target="#n2723"/>。化事畢，復問其處，<lb
ed="T" n="0845b20"/>僧曰：「是地古德甞止，國贈<persName key="A010399">金光照大師</persName>，名<lb
ed="T" n="0845b21"/>節孤<anchor xml:id="beg0845003"/>峻<anchor xml:id="end0845003"/>，神異不測，載錄圖記，人具爾瞻。」<persName key="A004846">遇</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0845b22"/>悲喜交感，久而不已，始結茅茲地，滌慮澄<lb
ed="T" n="0845b23"/>神，入三摩呬多<ptr target="#n1899"/>四十九日，鳥排<anchor xml:id="beg0845sgsz3"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0845sgsz3"/>雨，人萃<lb
ed="T" n="0845b24"/>香雲<ptr target="#n2724"/>，揚袂摳衣，歸依若市。乃剏興佛廟僧<lb
ed="T" n="0845b25"/>宇，十有七年不下山頂。日以《九會雜<anchor xml:id="beg0845sgsz5"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0845sgsz5"/>》<ptr target="#n2725"/>、《五<lb
ed="T" n="0845b26"/>部》<ptr target="#n2722"/>等法，翫味精課，不遺寸陰。覺聖力潛通，<lb
ed="T" n="0845b27"/>道出凡境，事或<anchor xml:id="beg0845sgsz7"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0845sgsz7"/>問，他見莫尋。士嚮庶歸，克<lb
ed="T" n="0845b28"/>念如聖。洎<persName key="A006571">懿皇</persName>運末<ptr target="#n2728"/>，<persName key="A004846">遇</persName>易舊規，或拊掌大<lb
ed="T" n="0845b29"/>咍，或擊石異語，類<persName key="A003064">不輕</persName>之海記<ptr target="#n2726"/>，同<placeName key="PL000000023022">楚</placeName>客之<pb ed="T" n="0845c" xml:id="T50.2061.0845c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0845c01"/>佯狂<ptr target="#n2727"/>。及禍發<placeName key="PL000000000214">中原</placeName>，寇盜交騁，夷撤宮<anchor xml:id="beg0845sgsz9"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>壺</sic><corr>壼</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0845sgsz9"/>，鑾<lb
ed="T" n="0845c02"/>輅蒙塵<ptr target="#n981"/>，因省<ref type="person" target="#A004846">師</ref>言，其若合契矣<ptr target="#n2729"/>。時屬<placeName key="PL000000003797">河東</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0845c03"/><persName key="A009891">武皇</persName>遙嚮真德，就山致信。迨<date from-iso="+0888-05-19" key="j20455352045563" to-iso="+0888-06-16"><name>文德</name>元年夏<lb
ed="T" n="0845c04"/>四月</date>，命<placeName key="PL000000003871">憲州</placeName>刺史<persName key="A012809">馬師素</persName>傳意邀請，<persName key="A004846">遇</persName>曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0845c05"/>「浮世之寵辱，<ref type="person" target="#A004846">我</ref>何累哉？」堅拒遠徵，確乎不拔。<lb
ed="T" n="0845c06"/>以<date key="j20456402045640" when-iso="+0888-09-01">其年<anchor xml:id="beg0845sgsz11"/>七<anchor xml:id="end0845sgsz11"/>月十八日</date>，召門弟子曰：「爾可檢<lb
ed="T" n="0845c07"/>護戒足，好住餘生，<ref type="person" target="#A004846">吾</ref>與汝決矣。」言訖，儼然<lb
ed="T" n="0845c08"/>蟬蛻，俗歲七十二，僧夏五十一。門人<persName key="A012812">太文</persName>等<lb
ed="T" n="0845c09"/>哀慟哽絕。<date key="j20459062045906" when-iso="+0889-05-25"><name>龍紀</name>初祀四月十八日</date>闍維，獲設<lb
ed="T" n="0845c10"/>利羅凡數十粒。<persName key="A012812">文<roleName>公</roleName></persName>堅貯孝思，旌建靈塔，<lb
ed="T" n="0845c11"/>銜哀出入，投詣天府。<persName key="A009891">武皇</persName>賵<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1773"/>贈加等，文武<lb
ed="T" n="0845c12"/>崇烈，及<placeName key="PL000000006137">嵐</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000003871">憲</placeName>等州牧守，例刻清俸，俾助良<lb
ed="T" n="0845c13"/>因，建乎墳塔。即以<date key="j20460612046061" when-iso="+0889-10-27">九月二十五日</date>封窆基<lb
ed="T" n="0845c14"/>𡑞也。</p>
